    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is an incredible opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition! Meticulously maintained and looking absolutely brand new, it drives as flawlessly as the day it was first sold. It's a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and wants a car that has been cared for with the utmost attention to detail.",
